WEBVTT

00:08:59.770 --> 00:09:02.970
Vaccine giống những loại thuốc khác, 


00:09:02.970 --> 00:09:05.970
có thể có tác dụng phụ.

00:09:05.970 --> 00:09:08.480
Phần lớn là nhẹ và tạm thời

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:12.740
Nhưng những lợi ích thì lớn hơn 


00:09:12.740 --> 00:09:15.740
những triệu chứng phụ.

00:09:15.740 --> 00:09:17.300
Khi bệnh, chúng ta muốn 


00:09:17.300 --> 00:09:20.300
khỏi nhanh chóng.

00:09:20.300 --> 00:09:22.420
Nhiều người trong số ở đây

00:09:22.420 --> 00:09:23.420
dùng thuốc kháng sinh 


00:09:23.420 --> 00:09:26.090
khi bị nhiễm trùng.

00:09:26.090 --> 00:09:29.270
dùng thuốc huyết áp 
khi bị huyết áp cao.

00:09:29.270 --> 00:09:30.270
Chúng ta dùng thuốc trợ tim.